---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Verdandi Weaver — Returning to grounded wholeness
description: A calm body of work exploring how we become more whole, not by rising above our humanity, but by returning to the body, the heart, relationship, and the living world.
permalink: /index.html
ogTitle: "Returning to grounded wholeness"
ogDescription: "Soul, nervous system, body, relationship, and the living world."
ogImage: /assets/uploads/returning-to-grounded-wholeness.png
---
{% from "social-icons.njk" import icon %}

<section class="hero container fade-up">
  <p class="t-eyebrow hero__eyebrow">Verdandi Weaver · A space for soul presence</p>
  <h1 class="t-h1 hero__title t-balance">Returning to grounded wholeness</h1>
  <p class="t-lead hero__lead t-pretty">A calm body of work exploring how we become more whole, not by rising above our humanity, but by returning to the body, the heart, relationship, and the living world.</p>

  <div class="orb" aria-hidden="true" style="margin-top: var(--sp-7);">
    <div class="orb__ring"></div>
    <div class="orb__ring orb__ring--2"></div>
    <div class="orb__ring orb__ring--3"></div>
    <div class="orb__core"></div>
    <span class="orb__dot" style="top: 12%; left: 50%;"></span>
    <span class="orb__dot" style="top: 50%; left: 90%; animation-delay: 1.2s;"></span>
    <span class="orb__dot" style="top: 88%; left: 50%; animation-delay: 2s;"></span>
    <span class="orb__dot" style="top: 50%; left: 10%; animation-delay: 0.6s;"></span>
  </div>

  <div style="display:flex; gap: var(--sp-3); justify-content:center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: var(--sp-7);">
    <a class="btn" href="/books.html">Explore the Books</a>
    <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="/self-scans.html">Begin a Self-Scan</a>
    <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="/frameworks.html">Read the Frameworks</a>
  </div>
</section>

{% set latestEpisode = collections.rethinkingEpisodeEN | sort(true, false, "data.number") | first %}
{% if latestEpisode %}
<section class="section compact fade-up">
  <div class="container narrow center-text">
    <a class="new-episode-strip" href="/rethinking-society/episodes/{{ latestEpisode.data.slug }}/">
      <span class="new-episode-strip__badge">New episode out</span>
      <span class="new-episode-strip__title">{{ latestEpisode.data.title }}</span>
      <span class="new-episode-strip__cta">Watch →</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

<section class="section compact fade-up">
  <div class="container narrow center-text">
    <p class="t-lead t-pretty">This work is for people who feel deeply, question inherited ways of living, or sense that healing, spirituality, society, and the living world cannot be understood separately.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--sunk fade-up">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="section-header">
      <p class="t-eyebrow">The core idea</p>
      <h2 class="t-h2 t-balance">A human being is a living system, growing inside living systems</h2>
      <span class="rule"></span>
    </header>
    <div class="grid grid-2" style="align-items:center; gap: var(--sp-8);">
      <div class="clearing">
        <div class="figure" style="aspect-ratio: 1/1; max-width: 460px; margin-inline: auto;">
          <img src="/assets/uploads/living-system-tree.png" alt="A watercolor illustration of a human figure whose body forms the trunk of a tree, roots reaching down and branches reaching up — one living system." loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="stack-lg">
        <p class="t-lead t-pretty">You are not a soul living above a body. You are a soul, in a body, in a nervous system, in a culture, in a forest of other living systems.</p>
        <p class="t-body t-pretty">Wholeness begins when nothing in you is left out — when the parts stop competing for who gets to be real, and the roots, trunk, and canopy remember they are one tree.</p>
        <p class="t-body t-pretty"><em>You are not separate from what you grow inside.</em></p>
        <a class="link-chev" href="/frameworks.html">Read the full framework</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section fade-up">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="section-header">
      <p class="t-eyebrow">Ways in</p>
      <h2 class="t-h2 t-balance">Choose a doorway</h2>
    </header>
    <div class="grid grid-3">
      <article class="card">
        <div class="card__body">
          <p class="t-eyebrow">A library</p>
          <h3 class="t-h3">Books</h3>
          <p class="t-body t-pretty">Slow reading for grounded awakening, being human, belonging, and the long return to oneself.</p>
          <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="/books.html" style="margin-top:auto;">Explore the books</a>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <div class="card__body">
          <p class="t-eyebrow">Reflection tools</p>
          <h3 class="t-h3">Self-Scans</h3>
          <p class="t-body t-pretty">Gentle reflection tools for noticing what is happening within you. They do not diagnose, score, or tell you who you are.</p>
          <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="/self-scans.html" style="margin-top:auto;">Begin a self-scan</a>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <div class="card__body">
          <p class="t-eyebrow">Maps for being human</p>
          <h3 class="t-h3">Frameworks</h3>
          <p class="t-body t-pretty">Visual maps for understanding the larger patterns shaping inner life, relationships, culture, and the world around us.</p>
          <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="/frameworks.html" style="margin-top:auto;">Explore the frameworks</a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--sunk fade-up">
  <div class="container narrow center-text">
    <p class="t-eyebrow">Essays &amp; talks</p>
    <h2 class="t-h2 t-balance">Reflections and conversations</h2>
    <p class="t-lead t-pretty" style="margin-top: var(--sp-4);">Essays, short films, and longer talks about nervous systems, awakening, emotional ecology, society, and the work of becoming more human.</p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap: var(--sp-3); justify-content:center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: var(--sp-6);">
      <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="/articles.html">Read reflections</a>
      <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="/videos.html">Watch videos</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% set substackItems = collections.substackFeed %}
<section class="section section--sunk fade-up" id="latest-from-verdandi-weaver">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="section-header">
      <p class="t-eyebrow">What is growing now</p>
      <h2 class="t-h2 t-balance">Latest from Verdandi Weaver</h2>
      <p class="t-lead t-pretty">New podcast episodes, films, reflections, resources, and ways to follow or support the work.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="center-text">
      <p class="t-eyebrow">Latest listening</p>
      <p class="t-body t-pretty" style="max-width: 56ch; margin: var(--sp-2) auto 0;">Reflections on being human, society, spirit, science, and the strange beauty of everything in between.</p>
    </div>

    {% if substackItems.length %}
      <div class="grid grid-2" style="align-items:center; gap: var(--sp-7); margin-top: var(--sp-7);">
        <div class="clearing">
          <div class="figure" style="aspect-ratio: 4/5; max-width: 380px; margin-inline: auto;">
            <img src="/assets/uploads/returning-to-grounded-wholeness.png" alt="Verdandi Weaver — a calm branded image, shown here since this episode has no artwork of its own" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="new-episode-strip__badge" style="display:inline-block;">Newest episode</span>
          <h3 class="t-h3" style="margin-top: var(--sp-3);">{{ substackItems[0].title }}</h3>
          {% if substackItems[0].description %}<p class="t-body t-pretty" style="margin-top: var(--sp-2);">{{ substackItems[0].description }}</p>{% endif %}
          {% if substackItems[0].date %}<p class="t-meta" style="margin-top: var(--sp-3);"><time datetime="{{ substackItems[0].date }}">{{ substackItems[0].date | date("DD MMMM YYYY") }}</time></p>{% endif %}
          <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="{{ substackItems[0].url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="margin-top: var(--sp-5);">Listen to the episode →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      {% if substackItems.length > 1 %}
      <div class="listening-row" style="margin-top: var(--sp-8);">
        {% for item in substackItems %}
          {% if not loop.first %}
          <a class="listening-row__item" href="{{ item.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            {% if item.date %}<p class="t-meta"><time datetime="{{ item.date }}">{{ item.date | date("DD MMMM YYYY") }}</time></p>{% endif %}
            <h4 class="t-h4 listening-row__title" style="margin-top: var(--sp-2);">{{ item.title }}</h4>
            {% if item.description %}<p class="t-meta" style="margin-top: var(--sp-1);">{{ item.description }}</p>{% endif %}
          </a>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% endif %}

      <div class="center-text" style="margin-top: var(--sp-7);">
        <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="{{ links.substack }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Read and listen on Substack →</a>
      </div>
    {% else %}
      <div class="center-text" style="margin-top: var(--sp-6);">
        <p class="t-body t-pretty">New episodes are available on Substack.</p>
        <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="{{ links.substack }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="margin-top: var(--sp-4);">Visit Verdandi Weaver on Substack</a>
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    <span class="growing-divider"></span>

    <div class="center-text">
      <p class="t-eyebrow">Follow along</p>
      <h3 class="t-h3" style="margin-top: var(--sp-2);">Find the work wherever you already listen, watch, read, or gather.</h3>
      <div class="social-row" style="margin-top: var(--sp-6);">
        {% for p in socialPlatforms %}
        <a class="social-row__item" href="{{ p.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="{{ p.name }} — {{ p.descriptor }} (opens in a new tab)">
          <span class="social-row__icon">{{ icon(p.icon) }}</span>
          <span class="social-row__text">
            <span class="social-row__name">{{ p.name }}</span>
            <span class="social-row__descriptor">{{ p.descriptor }}</span>
          </span>
        </a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <span class="growing-divider"></span>

    <div class="center-text">
      <p class="t-eyebrow">Help this work continue</p>
      <h3 class="t-h3" style="margin-top: var(--sp-2);">Verdandi Weaver is independently created</h3>
      <p class="t-body t-pretty" style="max-width: 60ch; margin: var(--sp-3) auto 0;">Support helps make space for new podcast episodes, films, books, reflection tools, translations, subtitles, Rethinking Society resources, and future online gatherings.</p>
      <div class="grid grid-3" style="margin-top: var(--sp-7); text-align: left;">
        {% for s in supportPlatforms %}
        <div>
          <span class="support-card__icon">{{ icon(s.icon) }}</span>
          <h4 class="t-h4" style="margin-top: var(--sp-3);">{{ s.name }}</h4>
          <p class="t-body t-pretty" style="margin-top: var(--sp-2);">{{ s.description }}</p>
          <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="{{ s.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="margin-top: var(--sp-4);">{{ s.buttonText }}</a>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

{% if substackItems.length %}
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "PodcastEpisode",
  "name": {{ substackItems[0].title | dump | safe }},
  "url": {{ substackItems[0].url | dump | safe }},
  {% if substackItems[0].date %}"datePublished": {{ substackItems[0].date | dump | safe }},{% endif %}
  "partOfSeries": {
    "@type": "PodcastSeries",
    "name": "Verdandi Weaver",
    "url": "https://novaharmonia.substack.com/"
  }
}
</script>
{% endif %}

<section class="section fade-up">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="section-header">
      <p class="t-eyebrow">How it fits together</p>
      <h2 class="t-h2 t-balance">A living body of work</h2>
    </header>
    <div class="stack center-text" style="max-width: 480px; margin-inline: auto;">
      <p class="t-body">The books hold the deeper journeys.</p>
      <p class="t-body">The frameworks offer orientation.</p>
      <p class="t-body">The self-scans create places to pause.</p>
      <p class="t-body">The guides help bring reflection into ordinary life.</p>
      <p class="t-body">The videos open the conversation outward.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="eco" style="margin-top: var(--sp-6);">
      <div class="eco__node"><span class="eco__dot"></span><h4 class="t-h4">Books &amp; writings</h4></div>
      <div class="eco__node"><span class="eco__dot"></span><h4 class="t-h4">Self-scans</h4></div>
      <div class="eco__node"><span class="eco__dot"></span><h4 class="t-h4">Frameworks</h4></div>
      <div class="eco__node"><span class="eco__dot"></span><h4 class="t-h4">Guides &amp; PDFs</h4><p class="t-meta" style="font-style: italic;">Growing next</p></div>
      <div class="eco__node"><span class="eco__dot"></span><h4 class="t-h4">Videos</h4><p class="t-meta" style="font-style: italic;">Growing next</p></div>
      <div class="eco__node"><span class="eco__dot"></span><h4 class="t-h4">Future spaces</h4><p class="t-meta" style="font-style: italic;">Coming later</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="center-text" style="margin-top: var(--sp-7);">
      <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="/ecosystem.html">Explore the full ecosystem →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--sunk fade-up">
  <div class="container narrow center-text">
    <p class="t-eyebrow">About the work</p>
    <span class="rule"></span>
    <p class="t-lead t-pretty">Verdandi Weaver is the body of work of <strong>Sara Leidelmeijer</strong>, a writer and systemic thinker exploring how nervous systems, inner life, relationships, culture, and the living world continually shape one another.</p>
    <p class="t-body t-pretty">Her work brings spiritual questions back into ordinary human life, where insight must eventually become relationship, choice, care, and the worlds we build together.</p>
    <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="/about.html" style="margin-top: var(--sp-5);">Read more →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section tall fade-up">
  <div class="container narrow center-text">
    <p class="pull t-balance">You do not awaken out of being human.<br/><em>You awaken more deeply into it.</em></p>
    <p class="t-lead t-pretty" style="margin-top: var(--sp-5);">Begin wherever something in you feels quietly recognized.</p>
    <a class="btn" href="/ecosystem.html" style="margin-top: var(--sp-6);">Explore the work</a>
  </div>
</section>
